<!-- ============ 1. PROJECT OVERVIEW ============ -->
<h2>1. Project Overview</h2>

<h3>1.1 About the Company</h3>
<p>ThriveCore Technologies Nigeria Limited is a premier information technology solutions provider established in 2015, headquartered in Abuja, Nigeria. The company specialises in cutting-edge software development, comprehensive ICT services, cybersecurity solutions, and enterprise hardware configuration.</p>

<p>With a proven track record of serving over 100 clients across financial services, healthcare, education, oil and gas, manufacturing, and government sectors, ThriveCore Technologies has established itself as a trusted technology partner in Nigeria and West Africa.</p>

<h3>1.2 Website Purpose</h3>
<p>The ThriveCore Technologies website serves as the company's primary digital presence, designed to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Showcase the company's services and product portfolio</li>
  <li>Establish brand credibility and trust with potential clients</li>
  <li>Provide detailed information about each software product</li>
  <li>Enable prospective clients to submit enquiries via the contact form</li>
  <li>Store and manage contact submissions through a backend admin dashboard</li>
</ul>

<h3>1.3 Key Features</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Fully responsive design for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices</li>
  <li>Modern UI with curved-edge sections and animated interactions</li>
  <li>Floating pill-shaped navigation bar</li>
  <li>10 product showcases with interactive UI mockups</li>
  <li>Contact form with Node.js backend and SQLite database storage</li>
  <li>Admin dashboard for viewing and managing form submissions</li>
  <li>Scroll-reveal animations and animated number counters</li>
  <li>HD SVG social media icons (LinkedIn, X, Facebook, Instagram)</li>
  <li>Full SVG logo reproduction matching the brand identity</li>
</ul>

<!-- ============ 2. TECHNOLOGY STACK ============ -->
<h2>2. Technology Stack</h2>

<table>
  <tr><th>Category</th><th>Technology</th><th>Purpose</th></tr>
