<!-- ============ 4. PAGES OVERVIEW ============ -->
<h2>4. Pages Overview</h2>

<h3>4.1 Home Page (index.html)</h3>
<p>The home page serves as the primary landing page and provides a comprehensive overview of ThriveCore Technologies.</p>

<h4>Sections:</h4>
<table>
  <tr><th>Section</th><th>Description</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Hero</td><td>Full-height hero with headline, description, CTA buttons, and animated stats card showing 100+ Clients, 10+ Years Experience, and 6 Industry Sectors</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Clients Bar</td><td>Industry sector badges (Financial Services, Healthcare, Education, Oil &amp; Gas, Manufacturing, Government)</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Services Overview</td><td>6 service cards with icons: Software Development, Cybersecurity, Cloud Computing, Hardware &amp; Infrastructure, ICT Training, IT Consulting</td></tr>
  <tr><td>About Preview</td><td>Tech infographic SVG illustration with connected service nodes, company description, and core values</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Products Grid</td><td>10 product cards linking to the Products page, with ThriveSMS as flagship</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Why Choose Us</td><td>4 feature cards: Enterprise Security, 24/7 Support, Local Expertise, Proven Track Record</td></tr>
  <tr><td>CTA Banner</td><td>Call-to-action section with dark gradient background</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Footer</td><td>Company info, products list, company links, contact details, social media icons</td></tr>
</table>

<h3>4.2 About Us Page (about.html)</h3>
<p>Provides detailed information about the company's history, mission, values, and team.</p>

<h4>Sections:</h4>
<table>
  <tr><th>Section</th><th>Description</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Page Hero</td><td>Dark gradient header with breadcrumb navigation</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Our Story</td><td>Company overview with HD statistics chart (SVG) showing client and revenue growth from 2015-2025</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Stats Bar</td><td>3 animated counters: 100+ Clients Served, 10+ Years of Excellence, 10 Software Products</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Mission &amp; Vision</td><td>Two cards presenting the company's mission and vision statements</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Core Values</td><td>6 value cards: Excellence, Innovation, Integrity, Client-Centricity, Collaboration, Community Impact</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Key Milestones</td><td>Timeline from 2015 (Founded) to 2025 (A Decade of Impact) with 6 milestones</td></tr>
