</table>

<h3>5.3 Components</h3>

<h4>Navigation Bar</h4>
<p>Floating pill-shaped navbar, fixed 16px from top, centred with max-width 1200px. White background with border-radius 50px. Contains the full SVG logo (chevron + THRIVECORE + TECHNOLOGIES), navigation links with pill-shaped active state, and a gradient CTA button.</p>

<h4>Buttons</h4>
<table>
  <tr><th>Type</th><th>Style</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Primary (.btn-primary)</td><td>Orange-to-magenta gradient background, white text, pill-shaped, orange glow shadow</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Secondary (.btn-secondary)</td><td>White background, blue text, blue border, pill-shaped</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Outline (.btn-outline)</td><td>Transparent background, white text/border (for dark sections)</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Blue (.btn-blue)</td><td>Blue gradient background, white text, blue glow shadow</td></tr>
</table>

<h4>Cards</h4>
<p>All cards use border-radius 24px (--radius-xl), white background, 1px gray border, and hover effects including translateY(-6px to -8px) lift and shadow enhancement.</p>

<h4>Section Layout</h4>
<p>All sections have border-radius 32px with 12px horizontal margin, creating a curved-edge sectional layout. The hero and page heroes have top margin of 96px to clear the floating navbar. The footer has 16px bottom margin.</p>

